{"tid":1184464,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 發佈新 MacBook Pro","createTime":"2019-06-03T15:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T21:28:37.000Z","uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5706ecb278650c42de22077c4af7719a18a961b7","tid":1184464,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"Samsung 早前發佈一系列新 Notebook，外媒 The Verge 看到後直指 &ldquo;Samsung 發佈新 MacBook Pro&rdquo;。這款名為 Samsung Notebook 7 的設計，跟 Apple MacBook Pro 極似，分別有 13 吋及 15 吋版，如果不是看到有 Windows，後多人也會看錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金屬外型，圓邊設計，更有黑色及銀色可選，幼邊框、闊 Trackpad，更相似就是預設的 Wallpaper 以至鍵盤上的字型，可謂跟 MacBook 同出一徹。當然，真正的 MacBook Pro 有 Touchbar，而鍵盤兩旁有揚聲器。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，近年不少品牌也仿效 MacBook Pro 設計，而 Razer 的 Razer Blade 可算成功的一款。很多人會以 PC 界的 Macbook Pro 來形容 Razer Blade。相信 Samsung 的 NoteBook 7 也是想跟 Razer 一般以 PC 界 Macbook Pro 作定位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/005_Notebook7Force.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F005_Notebook7Force.jpg&h=8d5756ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/004_Notebook7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F004_Notebook7.jpg&h=4adfc541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9412274eef34294da137fcdf440652b1040942ab","tid":1184464,"uid":15835,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"iFanboy 寫一篇 Samsung 既文<br />\n可以寫五六次 Macbook Pro<br />\nMacbook 個設計又唔係有乜特別<br />\n仲要明明就好多地方都唔同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a268442d57f3407a6e3e7cd696d2902a67b8ea4","tid":1184464,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"行咩os先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4219e9f34635080a60fa3f28d17d1fc842d791","tid":1184464,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"Verge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865a2bc7e0f1f6009f459eba41043b0a4ddeace6","tid":1184464,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"唔會連macbook pro 個垃圾keyboard 都抄埋吧"},{"pid":"96161b0631ed3c28efd17ffb3e669e53f54ea79d","tid":1184464,"uid":169968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T19:39:21.000Z","msg":"好似？ 係咪傻左個腦呀"},{"pid":"aeafa616ee2525325ebf5ce85a355500d7319413","tid":1184464,"uid":256215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T20:35:05.000Z","msg":"又有屏幕又有keyboard ，似到。"},{"pid":"ea6bc96dd9a2f6f005ad07e10e7a0ec0c6a193b0","tid":1184464,"uid":231725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T21:28:37.000Z","msg":"呢部算好<br />\n睇下華為個部<br />\n連名都似叫matebook<br />\n屌佢老味唔知醜字點寫"}]}